quests.desc: Welcome to another life changing episode of TextWorld! Your first objective is to venture north. Once you finish that, try to head west. After that, go south. After that, travel south. Once you succeed at that, venture south. Then, make an attempt to travel west. Following that, go west. With that done, retrieve the chocolate bar in the cubicle. After taking the chocolate bar, head east. After that, put the chocolate bar on the desk. And once you've done that, you win!
